Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:06.92,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.64,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In this kingdom where magic is everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:10.74,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,there is one boy who can't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:12.05,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:16.62,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He puts in blood, sweat, and tears \Nin hopes of becoming the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:22.58,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But there are also those in the kingdom \Nwho possess at least a little bit of mana,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:26.73,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,yet can barely use any magic at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:32.38,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The very few out of the population, \Nthose who live in the shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:40.76,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They are also trying to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.94,0:00:52.29,main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.29,0:00:53.67,main,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:54.25,main,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:59.70,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,On that night in the Clover Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.87,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,when chaos reigned due to the \Nreincarnation of the elves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:05.50,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Dear! Mother! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:11.13,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Dazu, who lived in a town called Tiulyu, \Nlost her husband and mother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:23.35,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Along with another resident of \NTiulyu named Bow, she decided
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:26.19,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,to confront Kabwe, \Na member of the Magic Parliament.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:30.27,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Kabwe hated devils immensely,\Nand the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:35.57,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, Nero, and Marie, who were supposed \Nto be sentenced for being devil-possessed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:40.20,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,had their trial delayed by Damnatio made \NKabwe resent the situation even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:43.24,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They eventually took action.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:48.58,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They assumed the title "Devil Banishers" \Nand kidnapped Marie from the church in Nean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:52.84,main,Siona,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away again,\N servant of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.45,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not a servant of the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:02:00.47,main,Onoby,0000,0000,0000,,We must return the scale that's tilted\Ntoward darkness back to the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.69,0:02:01.49,main,Onoby,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:04.91,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:08.14,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother! Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.48,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Around the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:14.47,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Nero were put to sleep so \Nthey could be taken away, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:17.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:19.32,main,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:24.37,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from Asta and Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:27.12,italics,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Magic: Inverse Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:36.17,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My body... Crap! I'm gonna di...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:38.26,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.68,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Sea Dragon's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.65,main,Mask C,0000,0000,0000,,Plant Magic: The Flower on the Roadside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:42.97,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.09,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.94,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta! Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:51.40,main,Mask D,0000,0000,0000,,She's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Dragon's Waterball!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.11,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle stopped them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:01.38,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, Nero was still taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.45,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,And Asta....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:06.04,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.69,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Devil Banishers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:11.29,main,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,We wish for the demise of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.25,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away! Give Nero back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:17.43,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:19.69,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:22.29,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:49.22,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\move(315,115,315,110)\t(1,4650,\fs24)\fad(500,1)}The Tilted Scale
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:11.74,main,Onoby,0000,0000,0000,,I see you made it safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.27,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,How did things go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.42,main,Siona,0000,0000,0000,,We had no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:26.73,main,Onoby,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.14,main,Mask D,0000,0000,0000,,We apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:31.56,main,Dazu,0000,0000,0000,,Someone got in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:33.76,main,Onoby,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:36.23,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,But by now, he should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.60,main,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,in a deep sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:51.85,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How is Asta? He's still alive, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:54.74,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:57.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Then why won't he open his eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:02.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he's alive, what if he's under some \Nspell that will keep him asleep forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:07.64,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Asta's not \Nasleep because of a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.72,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:12.13,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The reason Asta's still asleep is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:13.55,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.84,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,What possessed you to bring \Nme here all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:24.53,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:27.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So the kid's still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:31.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, he's not \Nasleep because of a spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:36.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna suggest it's some \Nsleeping potion, are you, you quack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:38.54,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.45,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite surprising, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:47.05,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who did it, but to think \Nsomeone could make one this powerful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:50.30,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Why would anyone have a sleeping potion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:52.46,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,That, I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:56.97,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,If he just continues to rest for a while, \Nhe should wake up on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.36,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:04.98,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So since they put him to sleep, they weren't \Nplanning to kill him right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:09.49,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's see what exactly happened to Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.99,sign_18968_247_Heart_Kingdom,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}A Town in the Common Realm, Nean
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:20.04,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, you old hag! This is the third time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:21.62,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,The third time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:25.07,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That's how many times Marie's \Nbeen put in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:28.56,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,First was when these assholes took her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:31.97,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Then it was the trial, and now this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.90,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,The third time's the charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:36.05,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:39.63,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche! You shouldn't be \Nso rough with the elderly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.37,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You can shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.77,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't even about seniority \Nanymore! You're just rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:49.11,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this happened while I was gone,\N I have nothing to say in my defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:53.37,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't there something \Nmore important you need to do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:55.58,main,Theresa,0000,0000,0000,,before you try to strangle an old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:02.52,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Marie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.44,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! What the hell happened to Marie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.84,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:10.30,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me or I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:15.43,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,S-Some masked guys calling themselves \Nthe Devil Banishers took Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.16,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:20.55,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have no idea! But they \Nsaid something weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:22.77,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Quit wasting my time and spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:26.12,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was, "We must return \Nthe scale that's tilted
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:28.11,main,Neige,0000,0000,0000,,toward darkness back to the light."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:29.86,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Scale?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:35.91,flashback,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.12,flashback,Nero,0000,0000,0000,,Poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:44.12,flashback,Kabwe,0000,0000,0000,,Your mixing abilities are quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:45.96,flashbackitalics,Bow,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.90,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about some creepy-ass masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:57.56,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My body... Crap! I'm gonna di...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.20,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:05.69,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they sure fell for a lame-ass trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:07.44,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:11.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,their spells weren't that powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:16.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they did that so the other \NBlack Bulls wouldn't sense their mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:21.59,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably why Henry \Ndidn't wake up, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:33.21,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yami! Knock that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:36.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did these assholes attack \Nmy hideout while I was gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.97,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,they took one of my squad members, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:43.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who the hell they are, \Nbut they sure wanted to test my patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:48.25,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.67,main,Guy A,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman Damnatio, what was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:12.00,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Does no one in the Black Bulls\N know how to use a door?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.38,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:17.86,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Marie? Did something happen to your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.84,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.81,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I know you took her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:24.87,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.70,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You're really gonna act like you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:31.26,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not acting, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:37.22,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Considering everything you \Njust did, you must be judged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:41.40,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,You two should move back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.70,main,Guy a and b,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:49.71,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This is what he did last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:53.73,italics,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Scale Magic: Scale Regulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:58.23,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,You were imprisoned once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.80,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll have to send \Nyou back to that life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.10,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Just try it, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:06.14,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic: Reflect Ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:10.31,main,Guy A,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman Damnatio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:15.15,main,Gauches,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror Magic: Real Double!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.93,italics,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,He created a clone of himself with a mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:21.91,main,Gauches,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you! I saw your \Nstupid magic at the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:25.10,main,Gauches,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think we'll fall for that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:28.37,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you've underestimated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.36,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,On your knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.62,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:42.22,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Seize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:43.82,main,Guy a and b,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:57.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've been taking \Ngood care of my squad once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:14.88,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I know how much you hate him, \Nbut isn't this kinda out of the blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:18.67,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Also, who gave you permission\Nto use my wheels?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:19.98,top,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Wheels...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:22.79,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how much mana I had to \Nwaste to come here because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:27.08,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he just say it was easy as pie earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.10,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:32.85,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Because mole-chin over there took Marie again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.66,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:37.51,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Then who the hell did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:41.11,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I know those masked bastards said,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:45.57,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,"We must return the scale that's tilted \Ntoward darkness back to the light."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:49.11,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly the kind of bullshit you'd say!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:51.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say "masked bastards"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.16,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,And what if I did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You did, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:58.86,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see... I didn't see them myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:04.22,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It wasn't just Marie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:08.10,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to get the kid back, but Nero was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.10,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,So it {\i1}was{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:14.23,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot fathom how you \Ncame to that conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:17.31,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,First Marie, then Asta and Nero...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:21.19,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,They're the three that you put on trial!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:24.57,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You were just trying to take \Nthem out by force this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:28.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, I don't even care what \Nyou do to Asta and Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.32,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.27,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Give Marie back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:35.59,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Marx, show them my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:37.57,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:49.59,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Once my innocence is proven, you will \Npay dearly for your insolence toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:03.82,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,There's no memory that suggests \Nhe knew about the kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:08.61,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,It appears my innocence has been proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:13.22,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did you do all of this, \Nbut you accused me of kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:16.26,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,You will be taking responsibility for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:20.23,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Do whatever you want with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:23.38,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,But it's gonna have to wait until I save Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:27.38,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that was part of our deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.69,0:14:32.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:40.12,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That guy you were arguing \Nwith doesn't seem to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:43.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Is he so careless that he wouldn't \Neven show up after all this ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.78,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.33,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.40,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to butt in when things are so crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.99,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but there's something I'd like \NYami and the others to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.29,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.75,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,He should be there at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.30,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Begging your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.13,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.61,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The signal
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:15.74,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,is from the bracelet-type \Ncommunication magic item
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:18.48,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,that we used to track Asta's \Nwhereabouts at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:23.06,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,There currently seems to be a signal from \Nthe town of Tiulyu in the Common Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.76,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Someone took it off of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:29.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who know about the bracelet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:32.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,are the few who were present back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:36.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And the only one I can think of who \Ncould actually get it off is Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:42.00,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably trying to use the \Nbracelet to let us know where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:45.31,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's a good chance \NMarie's in that town, too. Fin—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:46.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Finral, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:52.43,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I've never been to Tiulyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Tch. Then I guess we're gonna \Nhave to use our brooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.24,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.81,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:03.12,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,My best friend's little sister \Nis basically my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:05.94,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Who are you calling \Nyour little sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:09.04,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait! This may be a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.60,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you stupid mushroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:11.40,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Mush—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:15.62,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it's a damn trap. \NIt's the only clue we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:20.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche's right. We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:21.12,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:27.00,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done talking to that criminal over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:28.44,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Read the room, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:32.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,While we're wasting time here,\N my squad members are—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.55,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Yami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:37.85,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I ordered the Black Bulls to \Nkeep an eye on Nero, did I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.26,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.19,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The Devil Banishers, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:47.98,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need you to get her back from that \Ngroup and continue watching over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:51.77,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd like you to postpone \N your judgment until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:54.19,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say, Damnatio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:55.75,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.29,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm counting on you, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:01.66,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:03.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're still not done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:08.72,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I know you probably don't feel great \Nsince one of your own has been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.92,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,But this is different from the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:17.47,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on what you do, you may be \Nputting your squad members in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:30.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go, dumbasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:31.66,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:33.93,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:34.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.87,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:47.83,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel, why are you helping us this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:50.95,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not lose any of the forces needed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:55.42,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,to eliminate the devil over \Nsomething like this. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:58.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're just worried about your \Nlittle sister, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:02.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to act all cool, Mr. Hubris.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:07.19,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Say another word and you'll \Nregret it, foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:11.70,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just say something about \Nnot wanting to lose any of our forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.07,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:23.20,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(984,1)\blur3}Tiulyu Town
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.07,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This town...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:28.78,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun must \Nhave come through here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:36.82,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:41.34,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:42.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:52.58,main,Siona,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is this another magic item that \Nblocks mana tracking, like this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:57.99,main,Onoby,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt we'll have to worry about anyone \Ntracking us out here, but just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:04.67,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,It appears they're doing what \Nthey can to block the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:07.61,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Did they find the bracelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:12.25,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,They might have. Either way,\N we should be cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we had to \Nland this far away, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:21.12,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:21.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:27.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just Marie and Nero over there. \NTheir kidnappers are with them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:30.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think will happen \Nif we just suddenly show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:32.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:33.88,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:37.28,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You got a picture of your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.26,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:42.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get any weird ideas! \NWe need it so we can ask around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:44.89,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.97,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,You better give them back when you're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:52.03,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:54.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:58.55,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Always watch your back. \NDon't go into the town alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:01.60,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the G-G Duo's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.92,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember teaming up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:06.55,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.15,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:09.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:12.56,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,So that leaves me with...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.46,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,A-Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:30.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It seems mostly untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:34.58,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,There are only so many forces we can \Nsend to help with their restoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:42.28,italics,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the damage here \Nwas pretty heavy, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:00.82,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:05.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I wonder how many \Nmore graves popped up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:08.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,after the Eye of the Midnight Sun attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:59.48,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:58.59,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:02.98,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Devil Banishers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:01.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Banishers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:06.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna get Nero and \NMarie back no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:09.05,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,From those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:10.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I think they were called...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:13.28,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Tooth-Pullers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:14.49,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Banishers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:16.59,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Stabbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:18.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Banishers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:20.24,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Fourth-Hitters!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:21.50,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Banishers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:23.88,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Night Train Passengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:25.25,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Banishers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:27.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Newspaper Reporters!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:29.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Banishers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:31.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Publishers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:32.26,sign_33783_322_Axed,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Axed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:32.26,sign_33783_322_Axed,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Axed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:32.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,For the love of... {\i1}Banish{\i0}ers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:34.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Banishers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:36.94,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling y—Hey, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:45.08,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Though I despise the devil, \Nthis country needs Asta's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.08,0:23:49.90,main,Some,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 144: \N"Those Who Wish for the Devil's Demise."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 144\N\N{\fs18} Those Who Wish for the Devil's Demise
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:53.63,main,Damnatio,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is trying to disturb \Nthe balance we have in place.
